#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2.000 parents<br/> ont confié leur enfant à notre crèche."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        For every kid"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Pour chaque enfant"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-door policy"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Politique de la porte ouverte"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Our mission"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Notre mission"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Un petit coin <br/>de paradis"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "À propos de nous"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Activités"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Toutes les activités visent à répondre aux besoins individuels de chaque "
"enfant. Cette approche aidera votre enfant à se développer au mieux de ses "
"capacités."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Contactez-nous"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nom d'affichage"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Confiez-nous vos enfants et partez travailler en toute sérénité"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Événements"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"Notre objectif est de rendre les premières années de la vie de votre enfant "
"aussi agréables, gratifiantes et positives que possible."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our goal is to create a safe and nurturing environment for your child to "
"learn and grow. We believe that every child is unique and should be treated "
"as such."
msgstr ""
"Notre objectif est de créer un environnement sûr et bienveillant permettant "
"à votre enfant d'apprendre et de s'épanouir. Nous pensons que chaque enfant "
"est unique et mérite d'être traité comme tel."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Notre équipe"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Notre équipe se compose de puéricultrices expérimentées."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Terrain de jeu"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Thèmes utiles"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"Elles proposeront à vos enfants des activités éducatives, ludiques, variées "
"et adaptées à leur stade de développement."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Venez nous rendre visite"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Nous vous invitons à venir visiter la crèche et rencontrer l'équipe à un "
"moment qui vous convient le mieux."

